183
00:15:09,341 --> 00:15:10,603
Hey!

184
00:15:26,425 --> 00:15:27,526
Your jade emblem!

185
00:15:27,526 --> 00:15:28,458
Wait!

186
00:15:43,275 --> 00:15:44,977
Sorry, senior.

187
00:15:44,977 --> 00:15:46,145
Did l scare you?

188
00:15:46,145 --> 00:15:47,113
No.

189
00:15:47,113 --> 00:15:49,281
Thanks for helping me back then.

190
00:15:49,281 --> 00:15:52,151
No. You were frightened by them
because of me.

191
00:15:52,151 --> 00:15:54,153
l should be the one apologizing.

192
00:15:54,153 --> 00:15:55,421
That's all right.

193
00:15:55,421 --> 00:15:57,556
l'm in a hurry. l have to go.

194
00:15:57,556 --> 00:15:58,921
Fine. Take care.

195
00:16:08,734 --> 00:16:10,292
What happened?

196
00:16:25,351 --> 00:16:27,114
What really happened??

197
00:16:29,955 --> 00:16:32,458
Father! Who killed our little brother??

198
00:16:32,458 --> 00:16:33,926
What exactly happened at our home??

199
00:16:33,926 --> 00:16:35,561
Why are there so many dead?

200
00:16:35,561 --> 00:16:37,688
Father! Why aren't you
saying anything??

201
00:16:39,165 --> 00:16:41,333
lt's not that l don't
want to tell you.

202
00:16:41,333 --> 00:16:43,102
You're still young.

203
00:16:43,102 --> 00:16:46,639
You shouldn't get involved with
some matters of our world,

204
00:16:46,639 --> 00:16:50,142
because you'll have a hard time
getting yourself out of them.

205
00:16:50,142 --> 00:16:52,411
Father! What's with you?

206
00:16:52,411 --> 00:16:54,470
You're not like this before!

207
00:16:54,980 --> 00:16:56,048
l don't care.

208
00:16:56,048 --> 00:16:58,175
Little brother was innocent!

209
00:16:58,551 --> 00:17:00,041
Shu Lien!

210
00:17:00,786 --> 00:17:02,947
l understand how you feel,

211
00:17:03,122 --> 00:17:05,357
and we must avenge for
our little brother.

212
00:17:05,357 --> 00:17:07,293
But now is not the time.

213
00:17:07,293 --> 00:17:11,127
There's still one very important
thing you have to do.

214
00:17:16,101 --> 00:17:17,363
Master.

215
00:17:20,072 --> 00:17:22,241
This will be our last escort.

216
00:17:22,241 --> 00:17:23,970
Let's get this delivered.

217
00:17:25,177 --> 00:17:27,008
An escort?! Now?

218
00:17:28,414 --> 00:17:31,440
l'm doing this as a favor for
a very good friend of mine.

219
00:17:31,617 --> 00:17:34,279
l've owed him much.

220
00:17:34,486 --> 00:17:37,323
Now that l'm retiring
from the martial arts world,

221
00:17:37,323 --> 00:17:39,658
l'm afraid l may never
pay back his gratitude.

222
00:17:39,658 --> 00:17:42,650
That's why we must
carry out this escort.

223
00:17:43,195 --> 00:17:46,565
Father! Tragedy has struck Hung Yuen

224
00:17:46,565 --> 00:17:48,834
and our brothers' corpses
are still warm.

225
00:17:48,834 --> 00:17:50,836
Now is the time for revenge.

226
00:17:50,836 --> 00:17:53,172
Yet you want me to carry out
an escort instead?!

227
00:17:53,172 --> 00:17:55,274
ls it because you want me
to stay out of this, father?

228
00:17:55,274 --> 00:17:57,476
Shu Lien! What's with you??

229
00:17:57,476 --> 00:17:58,911
Are you disobeying your father now?

230
00:17:58,911 --> 00:18:00,779
- But Father...
- Say no more!

231
00:18:00,779 --> 00:18:04,016
You have to carry out
this escort irregardless!

232
00:18:04,016 --> 00:18:07,119
We will sever our ties if
you refuse to do so!

233
00:18:07,119 --> 00:18:10,088
Then we will no longer be
father and daughter!

234
00:18:13,192 --> 00:18:14,660
Fine, father.

235
00:18:14,660 --> 00:18:16,321
l will go, since you insist.

236
00:18:17,329 --> 00:18:19,229
l need a room, manager.

237
00:18:19,398 --> 00:18:21,923
Sorry, but we're all full today.

238
00:18:24,103 --> 00:18:25,263
Senior!

239
00:18:26,405 --> 00:18:27,565
Little brother.

240
00:18:31,977 --> 00:18:34,546
Senior. You sleep on the bed.

241
00:18:34,546 --> 00:18:35,915
l can just sleep on the floor.

242
00:18:35,915 --> 00:18:36,916
Get some rest.

243
00:18:36,916 --> 00:18:38,250
l can't do that!

244
00:18:38,250 --> 00:18:40,386
Just consider this as
my apology to you

245
00:18:40,386 --> 00:18:41,751
for this morning.

246
00:18:42,121 --> 00:18:43,989
Your Excellency. You're
personally leading the troops

247
00:18:43,989 --> 00:18:45,691
to avenge our enemies this time.

248
00:18:45,691 --> 00:18:48,558
We are forever grateful to you.

249
00:18:49,228 --> 00:18:51,321
Let's get one thing clear.

250
00:18:51,463 --> 00:18:55,434
My sole mission is to eliminate
rebels of the Bagua cult.

251
00:18:55,434 --> 00:18:58,437
l have nothing to do with
your personal vendetta.

252
00:18:58,437 --> 00:18:59,505
Yes...

253
00:18:59,505 --> 00:19:01,173
Your Excellency is here for the rebels.

254
00:19:01,173 --> 00:19:05,303
But this Yu Hung Yen is also
one of the Bagua leaders.

255
00:19:05,544 --> 00:19:07,569
You must kill him first!

256
00:19:08,547 --> 00:19:10,249
Don't you worry.

257
00:19:10,249 --> 00:19:11,684
Once this is over,

258
00:19:11,684 --> 00:19:13,552
just hand over the list of the names.

259
00:19:13,552 --> 00:19:17,147
l guarantee you that Hung Yuen Escorts
will vanish forever!

260
00:19:18,257 --> 00:19:20,859
Little brother. Your kung fu is not bad.

261
00:19:20,859 --> 00:19:22,161
Where did you learn it?

262
00:19:22,161 --> 00:19:23,423
l'm from Wu Tang.

263
00:19:23,762 --> 00:19:24,990
Wu Tang?

264
00:19:25,497 --> 00:19:27,795
You know someone
from Wu Tang, Senior?

265
00:19:29,735 --> 00:19:30,903
Just one.

266
00:19:30,903 --> 00:19:32,338
Why don't you tell me his name?

267
00:19:32,338 --> 00:19:33,862
Perhaps l may know him.

268
00:19:35,808 --> 00:19:38,333
Little brother. Can you do me a favor?

269
00:19:38,610 --> 00:19:41,170
Of course, Senior. Just tell me.

270
00:19:41,747 --> 00:19:44,650
l have a friend for whom l'm
taking something to Wu Tang.

