Wu Tang and us

544
00:51:01,558 --> 00:51:04,995
had deteriorated with the
appointment of their new leader.

545
00:51:04,995 --> 00:51:06,553
But this time...

546
00:51:07,531 --> 00:51:11,297
That's why there are no
eternal enemies in this world.

547
00:51:11,568 --> 00:51:13,559
There are also no eternal friends.

548
00:51:16,106 --> 00:51:18,631
Those who can be used
are our friends.

549
00:51:18,775 --> 00:51:21,300
Those who can't are our enemies.

550
00:51:24,648 --> 00:51:29,608
Are they trying to mend
bridges with you, Lord Beila?

551
00:51:30,687 --> 00:51:33,155
ln the end, we're both
using each other.

552
00:51:33,423 --> 00:51:36,950
However...l admire their sincerity.

553
00:51:37,694 --> 00:51:39,218
Why's that?

554
00:51:39,963 --> 00:51:42,366
They are sending one of
their students here

555
00:51:42,366 --> 00:51:44,231
to offer me a precious gift.

556
00:51:44,701 --> 00:51:46,603
They're only a bunch of Taoist monks.

557
00:51:46,603 --> 00:51:48,298
What precious gift can they offer?

558
00:51:52,242 --> 00:51:53,766
Green Destiny Sword.

559
00:52:23,740 --> 00:52:26,334
''THE ClTY OF BAODlNG''

560
00:52:42,125 --> 00:52:43,490
Brother Yang.

561
00:52:44,127 --> 00:52:45,458
l'm sorry.

562
00:52:45,696 --> 00:52:48,265
l hadn't been able to
take care of the matters

563
00:52:48,265 --> 00:52:50,367
you bestowed upon me
before you died.

564
00:52:50,367 --> 00:52:52,803
l promise you that l,
Kao Lang Chau,

565
00:52:52,803 --> 00:52:57,240
will bring Xiao Fu here
to see you before l die

566
00:52:57,240 --> 00:52:59,042
so he can give you his offerings.

567
00:52:59,042 --> 00:53:01,244
You said the same nonsense
15 years ago.

568
00:53:01,244 --> 00:53:03,474
Looks like you haven't
changed one bit!

569
00:53:04,147 --> 00:53:05,444
Sister Lieu!

570
00:53:11,788 --> 00:53:13,690
You disguised as a beggar

571
00:53:13,690 --> 00:53:15,988
to avoid being captured
by the troops?

572
00:53:16,927 --> 00:53:19,229
You took my manuscript back then.

573
00:53:19,229 --> 00:53:21,026
Now is the time to return to me.

574
00:53:21,465 --> 00:53:23,456
l don't know what
you're talking about!

575
00:53:50,427 --> 00:53:53,697
Never thought a poor scholar
like you would actually

576
00:53:53,697 --> 00:53:56,233
possess such good kung fu skills
in just 15 years!

577
00:53:56,233 --> 00:53:57,601
Sister Lieu.

578
00:53:57,601 --> 00:53:59,336
lt's not too late to repent.

579
00:53:59,336 --> 00:54:00,667
Take care.

580
00:54:07,277 --> 00:54:09,312
We have to get more of these
silk fabrics in stock.

581
00:54:09,312 --> 00:54:10,247
Yes.

582
00:54:10,247 --> 00:54:11,448
They're selling really well this year.

583
00:54:11,448 --> 00:54:12,649
We can stock up a bit more.

584
00:54:12,649 --> 00:54:13,980
Brother Meng!

585
00:54:16,553 --> 00:54:18,384
Why can't you look at me?

586
00:54:19,189 --> 00:54:22,420
Miss, l'm afraid you've mistaken me
for someone else.

587
00:54:24,194 --> 00:54:25,593
Really?

588
00:54:26,296 --> 00:54:28,098
l am not some Brother Meng.

589
00:54:28,098 --> 00:54:30,534
My name is Chau Cheung Ching.

590
00:54:30,534 --> 00:54:31,601
That's not it.

591
00:54:31,601 --> 00:54:34,502
You're also the disfigured servant
at the Meng Mansion.

592
00:54:37,274 --> 00:54:38,775
Uncle Meng gave me this.

593
00:54:38,775 --> 00:54:40,037
Why aren't you admitting it?

594
00:54:42,045 --> 00:54:43,876
l just want to know why.

595
00:54:44,281 --> 00:54:47,117
You can annul our
marriage contract.

596
00:54:47,117 --> 00:54:48,285
You can even discard
our relationship

597
00:54:48,285 --> 00:54:49,684
and everything between us.

598
00:54:49,786 --> 00:54:52,186
But you can't lie to me.

599
00:54:52,622 --> 00:54:53,816
Shu Lien.

600
00:54:54,891 --> 00:54:56,825
Please forgive me for being selfish.

601
00:54:57,828 --> 00:54:59,386
Actually...

602
00:55:00,030 --> 00:55:03,022
l've never forgotten
my promise to you.

603
00:55:03,633 --> 00:55:05,624
l hate myself for doing this too.

604
00:55:07,137 --> 00:55:09,230
Don't worry, Brother Meng.

605
00:55:09,506 --> 00:55:11,641
l'm not here to force you
to honor our marriage.

606
00:55:11,641 --> 00:55:13,836
l just want to know the truth.

607
00:55:17,948 --> 00:55:19,347
Shu Lien!

608
00:55:19,850 --> 00:55:21,184
Where are you going?

609
00:55:21,184 --> 00:55:22,686
The world is such a big place.

610
00:55:22,686 --> 00:55:24,821
l'm sure l can find
somewhere to go.

611
00:55:24,821 --> 00:55:25,755
Take care.

612
00:55:25,755 --> 00:55:26,915
Shu Lien!

613
00:55:29,493 --> 00:55:31,620
Will we see each other again?

614
00:55:33,196 --> 00:55:34,663
l don't think so.

615
00:55:35,665 --> 00:55:40,534
Shu Lien, please stay.

616
00:55:45,675 --> 00:55:47,142
What did you say?

617
00:55:48,778 --> 00:55:51,941
lt's all my fault. Please stay.

618
00:55:59,389 --> 00:56:01,458
Did you enjoy your visit
at the capital?

619
00:56:01,458 --> 00:56:02,959
l would never have imagined
how the capital

620
00:56:02,959 --> 00:56:04,194
has changed over these past years!

621
00:56:04,194 --> 00:56:05,795
And l also had sugar-coated apples.

622
00:56:05,795 --> 00:56:06,696
lt's delicious!

623
00:56:06,696 --> 00:56:08,665
A lady of the mansion
eating on the streets.

624
00:56:08,665 --> 00:56:10,257
Where have all your manners gone?

625
00:56:12,602 --> 00:56:15,105
Good. Master Kao is back.

626
00:56:15,105 --> 00:56:17,005
He's going to give you a lesson!

627
00:56:18,041 --> 00:56:19,372
Master!

628
00:56:21,311 --> 00:56:23,747
Did you run amok while l was away?

629
00:56:23,747 --> 00:56:25,442
No! l'm not some wild monkey!

630
00:56:27,484 --> 00:56:29,119
Master Yuk, Madam.

631
00:56:29,119 --> 00:56:31,221
You must be exhausted, Master Kao.

632
00:56:31,221 --> 00:56:32,779
- l'm fine...
- Kao Lang Chau!

633
00:56:33,023 --> 00:56:34,490
Where do you think you're going?

634
00:56:35,392 --> 00:56:37,761
You're not getting rid
of me so easily!

635
00:56:37,761 --> 00:56:39,490
l'm staying with you for life!

636
00:56:40,096 --> 00:56:41,154
You...!

637
00:56:41,932 --> 00:56:43,797
Master Kao, she is...

638
00:56:47,204 --> 00:56:48,638
She's my wife.

639
00:56:48,638 --> 00:56:51,368
You damn scholar! How dare you!

640
00:56:51,608 --> 00:56:52,666
What?

641
00:56:52,742 --> 00:56:55,178
Do you want me to tell them
who you really are?

642
00:56:55,178 --> 00:56:56,880
Should l tell Master Yuk
that you are indeed

643
00:56:56,880 --> 00:56:58,615
the despicable, wanted
fugitive ''Jade Fox''?

644
00:56:58,615 --> 00:56:59,549
You...

645
00:56:59,549 --> 00:57:01,785
Master Yuk is the newly
appointed Viceroy.

646
00:57:01,785 --> 00:57:04,015
So you better be careful and
don't do anything rash.

647
00:57:06,990 --> 00:57:10,050
l want you to behave yourself
and stay here.

648
00:57:10,293 --> 00:57:11,228
Then...

649
00:57:11,228 --> 00:57:12,429
What about the manuscript?

650
00:57:12,429 --> 00:57:15,057
l will give it to you
when the time is right.

651
00:57:36,253 --> 00:57:38,221
You stole the
''Juo Wa Manuscript''!

652
00:57:38,221 --> 00:57:39,055
l didn't!

653
00:57:39,055 --> 00:57:39,923
You really didn't?

654
00:57:39,923 --> 00:57:41,291
l'll be damned if l lied to you!

655
00:57:41,291 --> 00:57:42,349
Fine!

656
00:57:46,830 --> 00:57:47,664
Are you still denying it?

657
00:57:47,664 --> 00:57:48,865
l wouldn't have stolen it
if you taught me.

658
00:57:48,865 --> 00:57:49,599
Still so arrogant?

659
00:57:49,599 --> 00:57:50,734
l must teach you a lesson!

660
00:57:50,734 --> 00:57:51,368
Master.

661
00:57:51,368 --> 00:57:52,168
Give me back the manuscript!

662
00:57:52,168 --> 00:57:52,969
No!

663
00:57:52,969 --> 00:57:54,170
Why wouldn't you behave?

664
00:57:54,170 --> 00:57:55,038
Because l'm not content!

665
00:57:55,038 --> 00:57:55,805
l have to learn it!

666
00:57:55,805 --> 00:57:58,205
You're not qualified to learn it
because of your temperament!

667
00:57:59,743 --> 00:58:01,044
Why can't l learn it?

668
00:58:01,044 --> 00:58:01,978
You're too wild.

669
00:58:01,978 --> 00:58:03,380
Just like l didn't want to
give the manuscript

670
00:58:03,380 --> 00:58:04,981
to ''Jade Fox'' years ago.

671
00:58:04,981 --> 00:58:06,516
lt will only beget more ills.

672
00:58:06,516 --> 00:58:07,584
Jade Fox?

673
00:58:07,584 --> 00:58:09,319
Master, so you know Jade Fox?

674
00:58:09,319 --> 00:58:10,754
She's your master's wife.

675
00:58:10,754 --> 00:58:11,888
She?

676
00:58:11,888 --> 00:58:13,256
She's Jade Fox?

677
00:58:13,256 --> 00:58:14,591
But she's really not my wife.

678
00:58:14,591 --> 00:58:17,661
She's here to take back
the manuscript.

679
00:58:17,661 --> 00:58:19,561
So this manuscript belongs to her?

680
00:58:20,297 --> 00:58:21,431
No.

681
00:58:21,431 --> 00:58:24,491
lt belongs to a Wu Tang
master, Jiang Lan Huo.

682
00:58:24,868 --> 00:58:27,063
Was he the one whom you
always pay respect to?

683
00:58:35,945 --> 00:58:37,003
You...

684
00:58:39,149 --> 00:58:41,384
Brother Jiang told me that

685
00:58:41,384 --> 00:58:43,720
he had always suspected
his wife Lieu.

686
00:58:43,720 --> 00:58:45,422
She's been eyeing the manuscript.

687
00:58:45,422 --> 00:58:47,481
So l've decided to hide it.

688
00:58:47,624 --> 00:58:50,427
This manuscript only has
the external stances.

689
00:58:50,427 --> 00:58:52,662
Lieu's talent and skills
are limited.

690
00:58:52,662 --> 00:58:56,132
lf she learns it, then she'll
only damage her own body

691
00:58:56,132 --> 00:58:57,801
and take herself on to the
path of self destruction.

692
00:58:57,801 --> 00:59:00,463
Master, then can you teach me
the internal stances?

693
00:59:01,271 --> 00:59:02,405
No way!

694
00:59:02,405 --> 00:59:03,473
Why?

695
00:59:03,473 --> 00:59:06,176
lt was greed that caused
your own master

696
00:59:06,176 --> 00:59:10,374
to steal the manuscript from Lieu
and learn it for himself.

697
00:59:12,582 --> 00:59:16,019
Even if my kung fu is now superb,
l feel like a thief.

698
00:59:16,019 --> 00:59:17,654
Always living in fear.

699
00:59:17,654 --> 00:59:20,623
The more my kung fu improves,
the more guilt l feel.

700
00:59:20,623 --> 00:59:24,081
ln the end, l had to retreat
to the deserts.

701
00:59:25,628 --> 00:59:26,796
Lung.

702
00:59:26,796 --> 00:59:28,131
Let's forget about all this and

703
00:59:28,131 --> 00:59:29,366
return it to the rightful owner.

704
00:59:29,366 --> 00:59:32,202
Master, you want to return it
to Wu Tang?

705
00:59:32,202 --> 00:59:33,430
Yes.

706
00:59:33,570 --> 00:59:34,404
No!

707
00:59:34,404 --> 00:59:36,506
Lung! Why wouldn't you
just listen to me??

708
00:59:36,506 --> 00:59:37,374
Master.

709
00:59:37,374 --> 00:59:39,409
l've already experienced
such superb kung fu.

710
00:59:39,409 --> 00:59:42,212
l won't be content if you
want me to turn back now!

711
01:00:02,565 --> 01:00:04,965
Greetings, Uncle Tak.
l'm Li Mu Bai of Wu Tang.

712
01:00:05,969 --> 01:00:07,527
What can l do for you?

713
01:00:07,704 --> 01:00:09,339
l'm a friend of Yu Shu Lien.

714
01:00:09,339 --> 01:00:12,365
She urged me to visit you
once l'm here in the capital.

715
01:00:13,243 --> 01:00:16,440
l knew what happened
to Brother Hung Yuen's family.

716
01:00:16,846 --> 01:00:19,110
Now she's the only one left.

717
01:00:19,315 --> 01:00:21,078
How is she?

718
01:00:22,085 --> 01:00:24,220
She's already found someone
who can give her

719
01:00:24,220 --> 01:00:25,778
happiness for the rest of her life.

720
01:00:33,797 --> 01:00:34,964
Morning, Madam Kao.

721
01:00:34,964 --> 01:00:35,832
Morning.

722
01:00:35,832 --> 01:00:38,460
- What a pretty bird!
- Let me tell you, this bird...

723
01:00:40,870 --> 01:00:41,738
Talk!

724
01:00:41,738 --> 01:00:42,906
Where's the manuscript?

725
01:00:42,906 --> 01:00:45,101
What are you talking about,
Madam Kao??

726
01:00:45,208 --> 01:00:46,609
Stop pretending!

727
01:00:46,609 --> 01:00:49,279
That master of yours must have
taught you kung fu!

728
01:00:49,279 --> 01:00:50,280
No!

729
01:00:50,280 --> 01:00:51,714
Master only teaches me literature
and calligraphy!

730
01:00:51,714 --> 01:00:52,578
You...

731
01:00:55,084 --> 01:00:57,253
You better stop lying
or l'll kill you!

732
01:00:57,253 --> 01:00:59,055
lt hurts, Madam Kao!

733
01:00:59,055 --> 01:01:00,323
Let me go!

734
01:01:00,323 --> 01:01:01,624
Still think you can fool me?!

735
01:01:01,624 --> 01:01:03,493
l really don't know kung fu, Madam!

736
01:01:03,493 --> 01:01:04,327
l really don't!

737
01:01:04,327 --> 01:01:05,385
Dammit!

738
01:01:09,232 --> 01:01:10,533
Miss!

739
01:01:10,533 --> 01:01:11,693
Miss!

740
01:01:13,470 --> 01:01:14,835
Old Master.

741
01:01:18,341 --> 01:01:19,899
What nerves!

742
01:01:20,343 --> 01:01:22,641
Who dares to hurt Lung
in my own house?!

743
01:01:23,613 --> 01:01:25,615
l'm not going to spare that person!

744
01:01:25,615 --> 01:01:28,418
The maid told me that,
when she saw Lung,

745
01:01:28,418 --> 01:01:30,286
only Madam Kao was with her.

746
01:01:30,286 --> 01:01:31,387
lt's her?

747
01:01:31,387 --> 01:01:32,376
Father...

748
01:01:33,389 --> 01:01:33,878
Lung!

749
01:01:34,023 --> 01:01:34,591
Lung!

750
01:01:34,591 --> 01:01:35,992
Madam Kao has nothing to do with it.

751
01:01:35,992 --> 01:01:37,093
Then...

752
01:01:37,093 --> 01:01:38,461
l was trying to catch a bird,

753
01:01:38,461 --> 01:01:40,656
so l climbed up the tree, and...

754
01:01:40,964 --> 01:01:42,261
ls that so?

755
01:01:44,100 --> 01:01:45,260
Master.

756
01:01:45,568 --> 01:01:46,626
How are you doing?

757
01:01:48,338 --> 01:01:50,670
Master, it's all my fault.

758
01:01:51,407 --> 01:01:54,069
l better return this
manuscript to you.

759
01:01:54,677 --> 01:01:55,769
You...

760
01:01:57,947 --> 01:01:59,349
You're right.

761
01:01:59,349 --> 01:02:02,546
This manuscript is
nothing but trouble.

762
01:02:04,287 --> 01:02:08,018
l think Jade Fox is not
going to let me go easily.

763
01:02:08,391 --> 01:02:10,859
Her kung fu is not
as good as yours.

764
01:02:11,127 --> 01:02:13,891
No matter what, she's not
going to give up.

765
01:02:14,430 --> 01:02:16,625
Besides, l was only doing it for fun.

766
01:02:16,699 --> 01:02:18,098
Forget it.

767
01:02:19,836 --> 01:02:22,566
How could you bully someone
who doesn't know kung fu?!

768
01:02:22,705 --> 01:02:24,207
l was wrong then.

769
01:02:24,207 --> 01:02:26,376
But you can't blame me
for everything!

770
01:02:26,376 --> 01:02:28,444
Had it not for you,
l wouldn't have done it!

771
01:02:28,444 --> 01:02:30,912
So is this really all
you want after all?

772
01:02:34,317 --> 01:02:36,819
That's Jiang Lan Huo's
Juo Wa Manuscript!

773
01:02:36,819 --> 01:02:38,650
Just take it and leave!

774
01:02:39,355 --> 01:02:40,757
This is too easy!

775
01:02:40,757 --> 01:02:42,358
l'm afraid you might
offend Viceroy Yuk

776
01:02:42,358 --> 01:02:45,020
if you keep rippling
the water here!

777
01:02:45,662 --> 01:02:48,264
A scholar will always be a scholar.

778
01:02:48,264 --> 01:02:49,666
Just mind your own business!

779
01:02:49,666 --> 01:02:51,691
Fine, l'm going.

780
01:02:51,868 --> 01:02:52,926
Then go!

781
01:03:03,846 --> 01:03:04,948
Madam Kao.

782
01:03:04,948 --> 01:03:05,682
lt's you!

783
01:03:05,682 --> 01:03:07,206
lt's late. Where're you going?

784
01:03:07,784 --> 01:03:08,808
l...

785
01:03:08,985 --> 01:03:10,316
You are leaving?

786
01:03:11,054 --> 01:03:11,986
Yes.

787
01:03:12,121 --> 01:03:13,089
l've told you.

788
01:03:13,089 --> 01:03:14,958
l'll leave once l have finished
my business here.

789
01:03:14,958 --> 01:03:17,126
That's all you have on you? lt's cold.

790
01:03:17,126 --> 01:03:18,923
Take this.

791
01:03:19,395 --> 01:03:21,431
Take care, Madam Kao.

792
01:03:21,431 --> 01:03:23,092
Please come back often.

793
01:03:24,867 --> 01:03:25,993
Wait!

794
01:03:28,371 --> 01:03:29,633
You know something?

795
01:03:30,039 --> 01:03:31,870
l'm not some ''Madam Kao''.

796
01:03:32,108 --> 01:03:33,405
l'm a bandit.

797
01:03:33,543 --> 01:03:34,711
Really?

798
01:03:34,711 --> 01:03:37,880
So don't be so nice
to just anybody.

799
01:03:37,880 --> 01:03:39,006
Do you understand?

800
01:03:45,588 --> 01:03:46,680
Madam Kao!

801
01:03:46,856 --> 01:03:47,880
What is it?

802
01:03:49,659 --> 01:03:51,991
Do you know someone by
the name of Lo Xiao Fu?

803
01:03:52,695 --> 01:03:54,128
You know him?

804
01:03:55,064 --> 01:03:58,001
He told me there's someone
who calls herself

805
01:03:58,001 --> 01:04:01,937
''Jade Fox'' that knows
who killed his father.

806
01:04:07,644 --> 01:04:09,236
You little fox.

807
01:04:11,681 --> 01:04:15,117
l almost fell into your trap.

808
01:04:16,552 --> 01:04:20,511
So you're just like
all the others.

809
01:04:21,224 --> 01:04:23,215
You just want to use me.

810
01:04:23,660 --> 01:04:24,427
Madam Kao...

811
01:04:24,427 --> 01:04:26,361
You know something?

812
01:04:26,529 --> 01:04:28,588
l'm not going to tell you.

813
01:04:29,232 --> 01:04:33,803
l want to leave a bait,
so that l may use you

814
01:04:33,803 --> 01:04:37,136
when you need me later.

815
01:05:15,578 --> 01:05:17,045
Do you hate me?

816
01:05:19,449 --> 01:05:20,750
l hate you!

817
01:05:20,750 --> 01:05:21,551
l hate you...

818
01:05:21,551 --> 01:05:23,519
Hate you...

819
01:06:43,666 --> 01:06:44,633
Dammit!

820
01:06:47,136 --> 01:06:48,304
Catch her, father!

821
01:06:48,304 --> 01:06:50,135
We have to revenge for mother!

822
01:06:59,982 --> 01:07:00,778
Father!

823
01:07:13,696 --> 01:07:14,560
Father!

824
01:07:14,864 --> 01:07:16,491
Father, are you all right?

825
01:07:17,066 --> 01:07:18,693
l'm not marrying a bandit.

826
01:07:18,868 --> 01:07:19,892
Why?

827
01:07:22,238 --> 01:07:24,040
l'm a Viceroy's daughter.

828
01:07:24,040 --> 01:07:26,108
Even though my father is no longer
commanding the frontier,

829
01:07:26,108 --> 01:07:28,344
l still can't associate myself
with the notorious ''Dark Cloud''.

830
01:07:28,344 --> 01:07:29,979
Even if my father doesn't object,

831
01:07:29,979 --> 01:07:31,614
other officials will
still suspect that

832
01:07:31,614 --> 01:07:33,775
he's conspiring with bandits.

833
01:07:34,383 --> 01:07:36,085
You're you, and your father
is your father.

834
01:07:36,085 --> 01:07:37,353
Why does it matter?

835
01:07:37,353 --> 01:07:39,651
Who cares where you go
once you leave him for good?!

836
01:07:40,857 --> 01:07:42,325
Leave him for good?

837
01:07:42,325 --> 01:07:44,452
l can't do that.
That wouldn't be filial.

838
01:07:45,094 --> 01:07:46,562
You can't do this and
you can't do that.

839
01:07:46,562 --> 01:07:48,120
So do you love me or not??

840
01:07:48,965 --> 01:07:50,733
Do l love you?

841
01:07:50,733 --> 01:07:52,360
You should know by now.

842
01:07:52,535 --> 01:07:53,661
Damn bandit!

843
01:07:54,237 --> 01:07:55,499
Then come with me!

844
01:07:56,072 --> 01:07:56,873
l can't!

845
01:07:56,873 --> 01:07:57,740
l don't care!

846
01:07:57,740 --> 01:07:59,173
You're being silly now!

847
01:08:03,212 --> 01:08:04,907
What's with you, woman?

848
01:08:05,381 --> 01:08:06,643
l'm not following you!

849
01:08:07,650 --> 01:08:10,915
So it's all because
l'm a bandit, isn't it?

850
01:08:11,254 --> 01:08:12,243
Yes.

851
01:08:13,256 --> 01:08:14,280
Fine!

852
01:08:14,690 --> 01:08:16,157
Then l won't be one anymore!

853
01:08:20,329 --> 01:08:23,633
l'll sever my ties
with my brothers tomorrow,

854
01:08:23,633 --> 01:08:25,567
then l'll come back for you!

855
01:08:27,403 --> 01:08:28,836
You really mean it?

856
01:08:50,459 --> 01:08:52,561
We should split here, woman.

857
01:08:52,561 --> 01:08:53,329
No!

858
01:08:53,329 --> 01:08:54,660
Let's go a bit further.

859
01:08:54,830 --> 01:08:56,161
Then go back with me.

860
01:08:56,365 --> 01:08:57,525
No way!

861
01:08:59,368 --> 01:09:00,733
Are you leaving now?

862
01:09:03,272 --> 01:09:04,796
Then give me a kiss.

863
01:09:06,075 --> 01:09:07,235
ln your dreams!

864
01:09:15,518 --> 01:09:17,418
You should go back now.

